{"tid":786603,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【求批】台北５日４夜行程","createTime":"2018-08-20T05:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T09:21:27.000Z","uid":15032,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"76f0b3dc865cc6a669f665adba66d5fc08afca3f","tid":786603,"uid":15032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"日日訓西門町<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一日)<br />\n夜晚到 西門町<br />\n<br />\n第二日)<br />\n<br />\nhea遊以下:-<br />\n岩行行耐D 唔岩就走<br />\n<br />\n午餐後出發<br />\n台北國際藝術村<br />\n華山文創園區<br />\n好休咖啡<br />\n誠品同松山文創園區<br />\nChubby Bird County 微熱山丘 <br />\n饒河夜市<br />\n<br />\n第三日)<br />\n<br />\n早餐後<br />\n去台北車站<br />\n轉台鐵去到瑞芳火車站<br />\n十分,十分瀑布<br />\n九份 <br />\n基隆夜市<br />\n<br />\n第四日)<br />\n<br />\n午餐後半日:<br />\n淡水, 老街 <br />\n搭船去漁人碼頭<br />\n紅26/搭船返淡水<br />\n士林夜市 / 寧夏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第五日)<br />\n<br />\n馬辣火鍋(漢口)<br />\n返機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主要想知第二日有無伏/推介<br />\n第四日 午飯後先去夠唔夠時間<br />\n茂園餐廳 雞家莊 瞞著爹值唔值得一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe73785500d624eb2082fda176efd0c511eb773b","tid":786603,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T17:25:32.000Z","msg":"大致正常合理"},{"pid":"8d410b1d4c1a91e1f98261d055b81873f669cb2b","tid":786603,"uid":12370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T08:30:50.000Z","msg":"瞞著爹好撚一般<br />\n入到去又多香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813138807190ba97a0e92138e4ccaa5533b6ecf4","tid":786603,"uid":107968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T08:32:53.000Z","msg":"去台北唔落club ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb64037b56a071b9884f88ece8cc40edd7af134","tid":786603,"uid":71063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"